 "Publish a form page on the web that takes an integer ",
 Cell[BoxData["n"], "InlineCode"],
 " and repeatedly generates a picture of a polygon with a random color and ",
 Cell[BoxData["n"], "InlineCode"],
 " sides."
}], "Exercise",
 Editable->False,
 Selectable->False,
